hits.definition:
北

[běi] north;

    东北 dōngběi northeast;

    北京 Běijīng

关 (F 關)

[guān] shut, close, turn off, close down, concern, key part;

    关系 guānxi connection;

    关于 guānyú concerning

内 (F 內)

[nèi] inside;

    内容 nèiróng content

{Compare with 肉 ròu meat and 丙 bǐng third}

加

[jiā] add, plus, append, (= 增加 zēngjiā) increase;

    参加 cānjiā join

由

[yóu] from, let, (= 由于 yóuyú) due to, (= 理由 lǐyóu) cause, reason;

    自由 zìyóu freedom

{Compare with 甲 jiǎ helmet and 申 shēn explain}

代

[dài] (= 代表 dàibiǎo) represent, (= 时代 shídài) generation, period, epoch, <classifier for periods>;

    现代 xiàndài modern (times);

    上代 shàngdài previous generation

入

[rù] (= 进入 jìnrù) enter, get into;

    收入 shōurù income

{Compare with 人 rén person}

先

[xiān] first, before, earlier;

    先生 xiānsheng mister, gentleman, Sir;

    祖先 zǔxiān = 先辈 xiānbèi ancestor

{Compare with 失 shī lose}

山

[shān] hill, mountain, <family name>;

    火山 huǒshān volcano;

    山脉 shānmài mountain range

五 (A 伍)

[wǔ] five;

    五月 wǔyuè May

太

[tài] great, very, too;

太太 tàitai Madame;

太阳 tàiyáng sun, sunshine

{Compare with 大 dà big}

水

[shuǐ] water, liquid, <family name>;

    水平 shuǐpíng level;

    水果 shuǐguǒ fruit;

    药水 yàoshuǐ liquid medecine

{Compare with 永 yǒng forever}

万 (F 萬)

[wàn] ten thousand, myriad, <family name>;

万岁 wànsuì long live

[mò] 万俟 Mòqí <family name>

{Compare with 方 fāng square}
